-belly/" ><img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/cbsny_pregnant_140924a-410x220.jpg" alt="" /><div class="gdl-caption-overlay" ></div><div class="flex-caption"><div class="gdl-slider-caption-wrapper"><h2 class="gdl-slider-title">WATCH: NYPD slams visibly pregnant woman on pavement, uses stun gun on her belly</h2></div></div></a></li><li><a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/colorado-students-walk-out-to-protest-conservative-censorship-of-ap-history/" ><img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Cutting-passages-from-a-book-for-censorship-via-Shutterstock-410x220.jpg" alt="" /><div class="gdl-caption-overlay" ></div><div class="flex-caption"><div class="gdl-slider-caption-wrapper"><h2 class="gdl-slider-title">Colorado students walk out to protest conservative &#8216;censorship&#8217; of AP history</h2></div></div></a></li><li><a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/stephen-hawking-comes-out-im-an-atheist-because-science-is-more-convincing-than-god/" ><img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/nbc_hawking_140924a-2-410x220.jpg" alt="" /><div class="gdl-caption-overlay" ></div><div class="flex-caption"><div class="gdl-slider-caption-wrapper"><h2 class="gdl-slider-title">Stephen Hawking comes out: &#8216;I&#8217;m an atheist&#8217; because science is &#8216;more convincing&#8217; than God</h2></div></div></a></li><li><a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/watch-grand-jury-declines-to-charge-two-officers-involved-in-fatal-walmart-shooting/" ><img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/John-Crawford-410x220.png" alt="" /><div class="gdl-caption-overlay" ></div><div class="flex-caption"><div class="gdl-slider-caption-wrapper"><h2 class="gdl-slider-title">WATCH: Surveillance video released after grand jury declines to indict cops in Walmart shooting</h2></div></div></a></li><li><a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/clemson-university-suspends-all-fraternities-after-freshmans-death/" ><img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Tucker-Hipps-r-via-Facebook-410x220.png" alt="" /><div class="gdl-caption-overlay" ></div><div class="flex-caption"><div class="gdl-slider-caption-wrapper"><h2 class="gdl-slider-title">Clemson University suspends all fraternities after freshman&#8217;s death</h2></div></div></a></li><li><a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/watch-gop-rep-blackburn-clash-with-cnn-over-ground-troops-to-fight-isis/" ><img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Rep.-Marsha-Blackburn-R-TN-092414-youtube-410x220.jpg" alt="" /><div class="gdl-caption-overlay" ></div><div class="flex-caption"><div class="gdl-slider-caption-wrapper"><h2 class="gdl-slider-title">Watch GOP Rep. Blackburn clash with CNN over ground troops to fight ISIS</h2></div></div></a></li><li><a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/twitter-users-mock-colorado-school-districts-attempt-to-rewrite-us-history/" ><img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Two-people-laugh-at-something-on-smart-phone-via-Shutterstock-410x220.png" alt="" /><div class="gdl-caption-overlay" ></div><div class="flex-caption"><div class="gdl-slider-caption-wrapper"><h2 class="gdl-slider-title">Twitter users mock Colorado school district&#8217;s attempt to rewrite US history</h2></div></div></a></li></ul></div></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="page-title-top-shadow"></div></div></div>                    <script type="text/javascript">
